ActForeign Missions and International Organizations Act
SubjectUnited Nations Peacekeeping Defence Ministerial Conference (Vancouver 2017) — Privileges and Immunities Order
PrecisUNITED NATIONS PEACEKEEPING DEFENCE MINISTERIAL CONFERENCE (VANCOUVER 2017) – PRIVILEGES AND IMMUNITIES ORDER in order to grant privileges and immunities to Ministers of Defense and other representatives of foreign States and foreign governments who are official delegates to the Ministerial, heads of international organizations and other official delegates of international organizations, and experts on mission for international organizations who will be attending the Conference in Vancouver, British Columbia, on November 14 and 15, 2017.
